Class Arm3Keyframe

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.marginallyclever.robotoverlord.arm3.Arm3Keyframe
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RobotKeyframe, Serializable

    public class Arm3Keyframe
extends Object
implements RobotKeyframe
    Describes the state of the robot at a given location. This is so that states can be compared, rejected, etc for collision detection.
    Author:
    Dan Royer
